---
// About Section Component with Profile Image and Features
---

<section class="px-6 md:px-10 py-24 border-b border-border-dark" id="about">
  <div
    class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-24"
  >
    <!-- left side -->
    <div class="lg:col-span-4">
      <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-32">
        <h2
          class="text-8xl font-black text-outline opacity-30 select-none absolute -top-16 -left-6 z-0 hidden lg:block"
        >
          WHO
        </h2>

        <div class="relative mb-8 group">
          <div
            class="absolute -inset-2 border border-primary translate-x-3 translate-y-3 z-0"
          >
          </div>
          <div
            class="relative z-10 w-full aspect-square overflow-hidden border border-border-dark bg-surface-dark"
          >
            <img
              src="/profile.png"
              alt="Edy Mikhael portrait"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2
          class="relative z-10 text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight mb-8"
        >
          About <br />
          <span class="text-primary">Me</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Fresh graduate from Mikroskil University, Indonesia. Passionate
          fullstack developer who transforms ideas into polished digital
          experiences. I bridge the gap between clean code and intuitive design.
        </p>

        <div class="w-full h-px bg-border-dark mb-4"></div>

        <div class="flex gap-4 flex-wrap">
          <span
            class="px-3 py-1 border border-border-dark text-xs uppercase text-gray-400"
            >Fullstack</span
          >
          <span
            class="px-3 py-1 border border-border-dark text-xs uppercase text-gray-400"
            >React / Next.js</span
          >
          <span
            class="px-3 py-1 border border-border-dark text-xs uppercase text-gray-400"
            >UI/UX</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- right side -->
    <div class="lg:col-span-8 flex flex-col gap-6">
      <div
        class="group border border-border-dark bg-surface-dark p-8 md:p-12 hover:border-primary transition-colors duration-300 relative overflow-hidden"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"
        >
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-6xl text-primary"
            >code</span
          >
        </div>
        <h3
          class="text-8xl font-black text-white/5 absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 select-none"
        >
          01
        </h3>
        <h3
          class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase mb-2 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors"
        >
          Fullstack Development
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-md">
          Building complete web applications from start to finish. I handle both
          the visual interface users see and the server logic behind it.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="group border border-border-dark bg-surface-dark p-8 md:p-12 hover:border-primary transition-colors duration-300 relative overflow-hidden md:ml-12"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"
        >
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-6xl text-primary"
            >sync</span
          >
        </div>
        <h3
          class="text-8xl font-black text-white/5 absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 select-none"
        >
          02
        </h3>
        <h3
          class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase mb-2 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors"
        >
          Adaptability
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-md">
          I learn new technologies quickly and can adjust to different
          workflows. I have a flexible mindset that welcomes change and does
          well in changing environments.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="group border border-border-dark bg-surface-dark p-8 md:p-12 hover:border-primary transition-colors duration-300 relative overflow-hidden"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"
        >
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-6xl text-primary"
            >palette</span
          >
        </div>
        <h3
          class="text-8xl font-black text-white/5 absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 select-none"
        >
          03
        </h3>
        <h3
          class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase mb-2 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors"
        >
          UI/UX Design
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-md">
          Crafting intuitive interfaces in Figma with a focus on user
          experience. Design systems, prototyping, and user-centered thinking.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
